  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Start of Your Turn] If you have 2 memory or less, set
    your memory to 3.[Your Turn] If one of your Digimon digivolves into a Digimon
    card with \uFF1CSave\uFF1E in its text, by suspending this Tamer and placing
    1 card from under one of your Tamers under that Digimon as one of its digivolution
    cards, reduce the digivolution cost by 1."
